{"tid":583912,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[$$] 梁洛施 VS 甘比","createTime":"2018-03-07T11:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-09T09:43:37.000Z","uid":82917,"like":17,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"dda5f306d3ec33f8615be879481d13d2156aa42f","tid":583912,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:38:37.000Z","msg":"伊莎貝拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n記者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢兩位真係城中典範<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n直頭要開班傳授港女「如何釣金龜分身家」<br />\n對比我女神大美人同埋邱淑貞個啲乜鬼豪門真係贏咗成條街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過Ada都嫁得唔錯老公又錫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 洪欣就咪撚提啦老公霉到名都唔撚認得，仲要拖住件同前夫生既仔受盡話柄<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n俾我做到佢地一日都好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實做徐子淇都好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/18.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">咪撚發春夢啦死港女，乜撚新鮮蘿蔔皮呀？有冇諗過竹門對竹門，木門對木門？成日FF釣金龜，我係有錢佬都唔會娶件無學歷mk臭串港女啦。照下塊鏡，醒下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":