br />\n大劉前日形容前女朋友呂麗君不要臉，其面皮厚過恐龍皮，睇錢比生命重要。</blockquote><br />\n恐龍皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"363aa86d96697825d2d36684998beaf9898744d8","tid":583912,"uid":23445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T12:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>甘比最幸福<br />\n大劉係老 但佢股霸氣好撚man<br />\n又肯駛錢嚮女人身上</blockquote><br />\n一出手就一橦The One, <br />\n好難唔man<br />\n<br />\nBtw,甘比個女最幸福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>聽佢鳩up都幾有娛樂性<br />\n<br />\n<strong>殯儀之星</strong><br />\n<br />\n02年，大劉現身拍賣會時解釋「殯儀之星」是他指某富豪喜歡出席有頭有面人士的喪禮：「譬如蓋茨（Bill Gates）有親戚死，有人就飛去西雅圖入殯儀館同Bill Gates影相，即係人有錢就死都要黐埋去。」<br />\n<br />\n<strong>黐枱王</strong><br />\n<br />\n大劉於02年大爆有「黐枱王」，他謂在超級富豪飯局中，有人喜歡黐枱博影相。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>專業小雞</strong><br />\n<br />\n02年呂麗君為大劉產女，但對被踢爆送樓給女友一事相當不滿，他直指放料者是「專業小雞」，對方過去曾花大劉近8,000萬元，如今不再風光，所以放料報復。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>華倫地牢</strong><br />\n<br />\n為愛將凌緣庭澄清與鄔友正拍拖一事，以華倫地牢譏某人自以為吸引。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>面皮厚過恐龍皮</strong><br />\n<br />\n大劉前日形容前女朋友呂麗君不要臉，其面皮厚過恐龍皮，睇錢比生命重要。</blockquote><br />\n恐龍皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n專業小雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c54a3c8cf2022371edab97caff1ba637c615a5","tid":583912,"uid":82917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"198d3ba06614649b1e539cf32b68647e93ea63fe","tid":583912,"uid":56716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-07T11:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想同大瘤做愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>吉妹，係都溝甘比啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <b